  "pages": [
    "铁砧以高速撞击一些特定的方块时，会产生特定的物质。$(br2)搭建一套环形加速器，需要若干$(l:power/large_electromagnet#acceleration_ring)加速环$()和$(l:power/large_electromagnet#deflection_ring)偏转环$()。$(br2)$(#888888)通过原版的堆叠TNT加速，水流防爆等机制，可以制作不需要电的对撞机，但较有挑战性。$()",    {
      "type": "patchouli:multiblock",
      "name": "建立环形加速器",
      "multiblock": {
        "mapping": {
          "u": "anvilcraft:deflection_ring[half=mid_center,facing=down,overload=false,switch=on]",
          "E": "anvilcraft:acceleration_ring[half=mid_center,facing=east,overload=false,switch=on]",
          "S": "anvilcraft:acceleration_ring[half=mid_center,facing=south,overload=false,switch=on]",
          "N": "anvilcraft:acceleration_ring[half=mid_center,facing=north,overload=false,switch=on]",
          "W": "anvilcraft:acceleration_ring[half=mid_center,facing=west,overload=false,switch=on]",
          "B": "minecraft:smooth_stone",
          "0": "minecraft:smooth_stone"
        },
        "pattern": [
          ["                       ","                       ","                       ","                       ","                       ","                       ","                       ","                       ","                       ","                       ","                       ","                       ","                       ","                       ","                       ","                       ","                       ","                       ","                       ","                       ","                       ","                       ","                       "],
          ["                       "," u  N             N  u ","                       ","                       "," E                   W ","                       ","                       ","                       ","                       ","                       ","                       ","                       ","                       ","                       ","                       ","                       ","                       ","                       "," E                  W  ","                       ","                       "," u  S             S  u ","                       "],
          ["                       ","      BBBBBBBBBBB      ","                       ","                       ","                       ","                       "," B                   B "," B                   B "," B                   B "," B                   B "," B                   B "," 0                   B "," B                   B "," B                   B "," B                   B "," B                   B "," B                   B ","                       ","                       ","                       ","                       ","     BBBBBBBBBBBBB     ","                       "],
          ["                       ","                       ","                       ","                       ","                       ","                       ","                       ","                       ","                       ","                       ","                       ","                       ","                       ","                       ","                       ","                       ","                       ","                       ","                       ","                       ","                       ","                       ","                       "]
        ]
      },
      "text": "这此提供一个样例"
    },
    {
      "type": "patchouli:multiblock",
      "name": "撞击室",
      "multiblock": {
        "mapping": {
          "0": "anvilcraft:cut_heavy_iron_block",
          "A": "anvilcraft:cut_heavy_iron_block",
          "B": "anvilcraft:cut_heavy_iron_slab[waterlogged=false,type=bottom]",
          "C": "anvilcraft:royal_anvil[facing=south]",
          "D": "anvilcraft:arrow[facing=south]",
          "E": "anvilcraft:tempering_glass",
          "F": "minecraft:redstone_block"
        },
        "pattern": [
          ["    AAAA ", "   AEEEEA", "   AEEEEA", "   AEEEEA", "    AAAA "],
          ["    AEEA ", "   AA   A", " CD   FAA", "   AA   A", "    AEEA "],
          ["    AAAA ", "   AAAAAA", "   AABBA0", "   AAAAAA", "    AAAA "]
        ]
      },
      "text": "撞击会产生一场大爆炸。一个由防爆方块组成的撞击室是必需的"
    },
    {
      "type": "patchouli:spotlight",
      "item": "minecraft:comparator",
      "text": "$(thing)比较器$()可以从偏转环读取经过的铁砧的速度(单位: m/tick)，并按一定公式转化为红石信号输出： $(li)32<V≤45.25 : 强度 9 $(li)64<V≤90.51 : 强度 11 $(li)128<V≤181.02 : 强度 13 $(p)公式：红石信号=$(br)2*[(以2为底,速度的对数) - 1] $(br)向上取整，小于0的都是0"
    },
    {
      "type": "patchouli:spotlight",
      "item": "anvilcraft:block_placer",
      "text": "检测加速到一定速度后，对一个拐角的$(item)偏转环$()施加红石信号使其失效，铁砧就可以从此处飞出加速装置，进入撞击室。$(br2)通过铁砧砸击$(l:basic/more_device#block_placer)方块放置器$()使其可以隔着墙壁放置被撞击方块；使用$(l:power/consumption#item_collector)物品收集器$()隔墙收集。"
    },
    {
      "type": "patchouli:spotlight",
      "item": "minecraft:anvil",
      "title": "撞击合成配方",
      "text": "撞击配方需要消耗被撞击的方块，需要铁砧的速度达到一定标注，部分撞击不消耗铁砧，具体如下：$(li)红石块+皇家铁砧(不消耗)(等级可更高)[>32m/t]→均8.5*$(item)铀粒$() $(li)飘浮粉块+皇家铁砧(不消耗)(等级可更高)[>32m/t]→均7.5*$(item)负物质粒$()"
    },
    {
      "type": "patchouli:text",
      "title": "撞击合成配方",
      "text": "$(li)$(item)负物质块$()+铁砧[>32m/t]→$(item)虚空物质$() $(br2)更多配方会在介绍新材料的合成方式时提及。"
    },
